Presumed Innocent;;67;;87;;R;;Prosecuting attorney Raymond Horgan (Brian Dennehy) assigns his chief deputy, the taciturn Rusty Sabitch (Harrison Ford), to investigate the rape and murder of colleague Carolyn Polhemus (Greta Scacchi), unaware of their torrid affair. When evidence implicates Rusty, Horgan's political enemies demand his arrest, devastating Rusty's wife, Barbara (Bonnie Bedelia). In desperation, Rusty turns to crafty defense attorney Sandy Stein (Raul Julia), only to be stunned by his trial's revelations.;;Mystery & thriller;;Alan J. Pakula;;1990;;Harrison Ford,Brian Dennehy,Raul Julia,Bonnie Bedelia,Paul Winfield,Greta Scacchi,John Spencer,Joe Grifasi,Sab Shimono,Jesse Bradford;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/presumed_innocent